{"type":"message","id":"0026ca45","parentId":"e2885a37","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:07:33.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user triggered a /new session reset. According to my SOUL.md and AGENTS.md, I need to run the Session Startup sequence. Let me check the relevant files as required.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md Session Startup:\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am (already in context)\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping (already in context)\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat): Also read MEMORY.md (already in context)\n5. Read session context: look for `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json`\n6. Read the most recent session summary: scan `memory/` for files with `*-session-summary.md`\n\nThe inbound metadata shows this is a direct webchat session (chat_type: \"direct\"), so it's a main session.\n\nLet me check the recent memory files and session summaries first.\n","thinkingSignature":"c56a50ceec3ed72685940189b12884cef331ffd6b2b30b8eeeef8489638b9f60"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_if6lm7m4c82t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_if6lm7m4c82t_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19746,"output":281,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20539,"cost":{"input":0.0059238,"output":0.0003372,"cacheRead":0.00003072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00629172}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776179242425,"responseId":"062d8b2a11e321a922ede97a974b8f96"}}
