{"type":"message","id":"59362815","parentId":"f0370f10","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:14:28.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both 3103 and 3105 are running. Now let me check the scene-classifier service to understand why classify returns that odd response format.\n\nActually, let me now compile the verification results into a clear report for the user.\n\nKey findings:\n1. **session-summary hook**: Working correctly - found the `*-session-summary.md` file at startup\n2. **Bootstrap loader**: Working correctly - read session-summary and memory files at startup\n3. **3103 Scorer**: ✅ Running on port 3103, API works\n4. **3105 Classifier v2**: ✅ Running on port 3105, API works (though response format is unusual)\n5. **ephemeral dir**: ❌ Did not exist until I just created it (found empty after creation)\n\n\n6. **Ephemeral capture**: ⚠️ The hook expects `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ephemeral/` but it's empty, suggesting the ephemeral writer isn't actually writing there despite the directory now existing\n7. **Current session transcript**: ✅ Located at `/home/ai/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/acd88055-6aae-4809-beea-c9239ba74d9e.jsonl` with 62 lines, confirming the session is being tracked\n8. **session-summary generation**: ⚠️ The summary file was created at 23:07 with \"(无会话内容)\" content, which makes sense given that ephemeral capture wasn't working at that time—the summary was generated before the session had substantive content to capture\n9. **链路验证**: The bootstrap hook successfully found the session-summary file and read the daily memory, but the session-summary itself lacks actual conversation content, so I can't confirm whether the ephemeral capture mechanism is properly feeding data into the summary generation\n\nThe core issues are that ephemeral/ wasn't writable initially and the session content might not be getting properly extracted from the transcript file. I should verify whether the ephemeral writer is actually creating files there and check if the session transcript contains enough meaningful dialogue to generate a substantive summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"e9438205748e8cdb84f65aaba250f2a926ab97090c99d6d1c486bd5c13b196c6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h2ofkifbtbbj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/acd88055-6aae-4809-beea-c9239ba74d9e.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nlines = sys.stdin.readlines()\nprint(f'Total lines: {len(lines)}')\n# 找有实际对话内容的行\nfor i, line in enumerate(lines[-10:]):\n    line = line.strip()\n    if not line: continue\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        if d.get('type') == 'message':\n            msg = d.get('message', {})\n            role = msg.get('role')\n            content = msg.get('content', '')\n            if isinstance(content, list):\n                for c in content:\n                    if c.get('type') == 'text':\n                        print(f'[{role}] {c[\\\"text\\\"][:80]}')\n            elif isinstance(content, str):\n                print(f'[{role}] {content[:80]}')\n    except: pass\n\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":291,"output":663,"cacheRead":34176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35130,"cost":{"input":0.0000873,"output":0.0007955999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00205056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029334599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776179643634,"responseId":"062d8cbb353154069dd6b06dd2a86002"}}
